026package org.jdrupes.mdoclet.internal.doclets.formats.html.markup;
027
028import org.jdrupes.mdoclet.internal.doclets.toolkit.util.Utils;
029
030/**
031 * Enum representing the names for HTML elements.
032 *
033 * @see <a href="https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/syntax.html#syntax-tag-name">WhatWG: Tag Name</a>
034 * @see <a href="https://www.w3.org/TR/html51/syntax.html#tag-name">HTML 5.1: Tag Name</a>
035 */
036public enum TagName {
037    A,
038    BUTTON,
039    BLOCKQUOTE,
040    BODY,
041    BR,
042    CAPTION,
043    CODE,
044    DD,
045    DETAILS,
046    DIV,
047    DL,
048    DT,
049    EM,
050    FOOTER,
051    FORM,
052    H1,
053    H2,
054    H3,
055    H4,
056    H5,
057    H6,
058    HEAD,
059    HEADER,
060    HR,
061    HTML,
062    I,
063    IMG,
064    INPUT,
065    LABEL,
066    LI,
067    LISTING,
068    LINK,
069    MAIN,
070    MENU,
071    META,
072    NAV,
073    NOSCRIPT,
074    OL,
075    P,
076    PRE,
077    SCRIPT,
078    SECTION,
079    SMALL,
080    SPAN,
081    STRONG,
082    SUB,
083    SUMMARY,
084    SUP,
085    TABLE,
086    TBODY,
087    THEAD,
088    TD,
089    TH,
090    TITLE,
091    TR,
092    UL,
093    WBR;
094
095    public final String value;
096
097    TagName() {
098        this.value = Utils.toLowerCase(name());
099    }
100
101    public String toString() {
102        return value;
103    }
104}
